name: Fed Up
description:
This game has the title "Themes of Suicide", as it contains theme of suicide. That particular wording, however feels way too harsh for a more comedic game.

The game has been retitled "Fed Up"

Arrow keys to move, 'Z' to jump.

Font is Oleaguid.
https://opengameart.org/content/oleaguid-font
The Oleaguid font was made by Arynoc!
